<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.11">
<l>kārvaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇapirāṉ kamalattaṭaṅ kaṇṇaṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yērvaḷa voṇkaḻaṉikkurukūrccaṭa kōpaṉcoṉṉa</l>
<l>cīrvaṇṇa voṇ ṭamiḻkaḷivaiyāyirat tuḷippattu</l>
<l>mārvaṇṇat tāluraippā raṭikkīḻpuku vārpolintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who speak with full beauty</l>
<l>these ten among these thousand [verses of] bright Tamil with excellent beauty</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr with beautiful fertile bright paddy fields</l>
<l>on the one with broad lotus eyes, lord Kaṇṇaṉ, the one of monsoon cloud colour,</l>
	<l>will flourish [and] enter beneath [his] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
